name: Twilight Client
tagline: A client for your bash profile.
body:
### Have your own ideas?
Get the current build's source code, and download and edit to your heart's content.

### Need an update?
Get some updates by simply navigating in your web browser to http://www.github.com/Twilight-Client/Twilight-Client

### USB Boot -- About it
It does not allow regular booting into usb.

### Support or Contact
Having any trouble? Contact (@mayers1) or (@andyman01) or even (@Twilight-Client).
